@unnumberedsec Other useful information.

For the following hosting services it is recommended to extend the maximum download limit
(add the @option{-m} option to the instructions listed above,
possibly indicating the maximum number of downloads to be made simultaneously
to proceed with the download in parallel, also through
the use of proxies

Many servers do not allow recovery of interrupted downloads and parallel downloading.
For these services ZDL uses Wget.

Some services require the use of RTMPDump (in its absence, but with limitations, of cURL)

The other services are enabled by default for Aria2.

To download from Sharpfile, Depositfiles and other services,
currently it is necessary to use the web browser to solve the
